WEBVTT

00:00:11.073 --> 00:00:22.751 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There’s trouble in the world, disunity.
No matter where we live, no harmony.

00:00:27.590 --> 00:00:33.554 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
